public interface DemographicFunction
extends org.apache.commons.math.analysis.UnivariateRealFunction, Units

This interface provides methods that describe a demographic function. Parts of this class were derived from C++ code provided by Oliver Pybus.

getThreshold

double getThreshold()
A threshold for underflow on calculation of likelihood of internode intervals. Most demo functions could probably return 0.0 but (e.g.,) the Extended Skyline needs a non zero value to prevent a numerical problem.
